To download the ilastik installer, please open the terminal inside your O2 Portal DesktopMate environment and run the following command:

'''
cd Downloads
wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/rkarmaka/DIOS/main/installers/ilastik_installer.sh
chmod u+x ilastik_installer.sh
'''

After downloading the file, go to your Downloads folder and double-click on the ilastik_installer.sh file. It would automatically download the installer, install ilastik, and create an icon
